GSD.description:
openvswitch: switch from WARN to pr_warn

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v4.9.332 by commit 636e16fa27f47cec5c97d1ecb52b03095fef15e0, it was introduced in version v3.14 by commit 44da5ae5fbea4686f667dc854e5ea16814e44c59. For more details please see the references link.
